Update: The scene has been cleared and the lane headed towards Mbombela is open. TRAC reported an accident on the N4 between the Matsulu and KaNyamazane turnoffs in Crocodile River Gorge. According to Solange Soares, TRAC’s spokesperson, a single vehicle (truck) overturned on this road. ALSO READ: “Tattoo” gives Jack Russell terrier new leash on life The lane headed towards Mbombela is currently closed and a stop-and-go is in place. The truck driver died at the accident. The scene is currently being cleared.